Effective immediately Please do not attempt to use the MedSource branded nebulizer included in the packaging with the CPAP. The DISS adaptor for O2 connection and tubing works as intended and can be used to supply oxygen for the curaplex branded Small Volume Nebulizer We have contacted the manufacturer and they are taking steps to correct this situation.
